TITLEXXX: Return of Xander CageSTARRINGVin Diesel, Donnie Yen, Deepika Padukone, Ruby Rose, Nina Dobrev, Samuel L JacksonGENREAction, Adventure, ThrillerRelease DateJanuary 20 This Triple X franchise couldn&rsquo;t have been better named. The Return of Xander Cage is just that. Xander Cage comes out of retirement to avenge the death of Agent Gibbons, who dies in a crash caused by a falling satellite. Cage and other Triple X agents go after the person who is causing the satellites to crash on earth. Full of inconceivable stunts, excessive fight scenes and unwarranted racy images, the film just about manages to capture the viewers&rsquo; attention. This film also debuts Bollywood actress Deepika Padukone in her first Hollywood crossover, as well as Brazilian football star Neymar Jr. Star Rating: 3/5